### ========================================
### 1. LOGIN - JWT token olish
### ========================================
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "api_key": "demo-api-key-12345"
}

### Response'dan access_token ni copy qiling va pastda ishlating
### Misol: eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### ========================================
### 2. PUBLIC - Barcha narx paketlari (JWT siz)
### ========================================
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/pricing/tiers
Accept: application/json

###

### ========================================
### 3. PUBLIC - Har bir slide narxi (JWT siz)
### ========================================
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/pricing/per-slide
Accept: application/json

###

### ========================================
### 4. PROTECTED - Narx hisoblash (JWT bilan)
### ========================================
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/pricing/calculate?num_slides=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### YOUR_TOKEN_HERE ni yuqoridagi login response'dan olgan token bilan almashtiring

###

### ========================================
### 5. PROTECTED - POST bilan narx hisoblash (JWT bilan)
### ========================================
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/pricing/estimate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "num_slides": 15
}

###

### ========================================
### 6. API KEY - Header bilan narx hisoblash
### ========================================
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/pricing/calculate-with-key?num_slides=10
Accept: application/json
X-API-Key: demo-api-key-12345

###

### ========================================
### 7. XATO - JWT siz protected endpoint
### ========================================
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/pricing/calculate?num_slides=10
Accept: application/json

### Bu 401 Unauthorized qaytarishi kerak

###

### ========================================
### 8. XATO - Noto'g'ri API key
### ========================================
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "api_key": "wrong-api-key"
}

### Bu 401 Unauthorized qaytarishi kerak

###

### ========================================
### 9. Token yaroqliligini tekshirish
### ========================================
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/auth/verify
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###